{
  "texts": [
    "In this section, we simulate realistic LSST WFD light curves, and assess how well EzTaoX recovers both the simulated interband lags and stochastic variability parameters.",
    "Section 3.1.1 describes the light curve simulation process and the sets of input parameters (see Table 1).",
    "In Section 3.1.2, we show that EzTaoX is capable of retrieving interband lags with accuracy comparable to that of JAVELIN.",
    "Section 3.1.3 and Section 3.1.4 demonstrates the robustness of EzTaoX in recovering input stochastic variability parameters (i.e.",
    "τ DRW and σ DRW)."
  ]
}